trans-unit.source: Stores legend cells in a LegendCellCollection object.
Adds a legend cell with the specified cell type, text and alignment to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션의 끝에 지정 된 셀 형식, 텍스트 및 맞춤 범례 셀을 추가합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LegendCellType"></xref> value representing the cell type.
A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents either the cell text or its image name, depending on the value of the `cellType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> 셀 텍스트 또는 이미지 이름, 값에 따라를 나타내는 값의 `cellType` 매개 변수입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"></xref> value that represents the cell content alignment.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"> </xref> 셀 내용 맞춤을 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: An <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""></xref> value that represents the index of the newly added legend cell in the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_integer" name="integer" href=""> </xref> 컬렉션에 새로 추가 된 범례 셀의 인덱스를 나타내는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: Inserts a legend cell with the specified cell type, text and alignment into the collection at a given location.
trans-unit.target: 범례 셀 된 지정 된 셀 형식, 텍스트 및 맞춤 컬렉션에서 지정된 된 위치에 삽입합니다.

trans-unit.source: Index of the location to insert the object.
A <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.LegendCellType"></xref> value that represents the cell type.
A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> value that represents either the cell text or its image name, depending on the value of the `cellType` parameter.
trans-unit.target: A <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> 셀 텍스트 또는 이미지 이름, 값에 따라를 나타내는 값의 `cellType` 매개 변수입니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"></xref> enumeration value that represents the alignment of the legend cell content.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.ContentAlignment"> </xref> 범례 셀 내용 맞춤을 나타내는 열거형 값입니다.
